prequel.translation[0].definitions[0].de: a book, film etc that tells you what happened before the story told in a previous popular book or film
prequel.translation[0].definitions[0].ex: ‘The Phantom Menace’ is a prequel to ‘Star Wars’.
prequel.translation[1].definitions[0].de: a book, film, play etc that tells an earlier part of the story in a book etc that already exists
